overview.longBusinessSummary: PSQ Holdings, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, operates an online marketplace through advertising and eCommerce in the United States. It operates through three segments: Marketplace, Brands, and Financial Technology. The company offers buy now pay later solutions through point-of-sale financing platform; and payment processing solution for its Merchant customers across their e-commerce landscape through PSQ Payments. The PSQ platform is accessible through its mobile application and website. the company also sells diapers, wipes, training pants, and soaps and lotions under the EveryLife's brand name. PSQ Holdings, Inc. is headquartered in West Palm Beach, Florida.
